00:30:58.039 --> 00:31:05.390
page, uh for SEO, that's a really smart move.
You know, um and the title tag as well, like

00:31:05.390 --> 00:31:10.980
you know, really you know for accessibility,
you want really easy to read title tags, but

00:31:10.980 --> 00:31:17.230
if you can kind of combine that with the proper
