00:31:55.559 --> 00:31:56.559
the project?

00:31:56.559 --> 00:31:57.919
[Joe] Uh for captioning?

00:31:57.919 --> 00:31:58.919
[Mike] Yeah.

00:31:58.919 --> 00:32:00.870
[Joe] I think it's probably a good idea to

