[Alexa] I'm not sure

00:32:03.380 --> 00:32:05.899
[Mike] Bye Alexa, sorry.

00:32:05.899 --> 00:32:11.941
[Joe] Okay, I think it's probably a good idea
to go ahead and um integrate some humid, some

00:32:11.941 --> 00:32:17.200
human editorial stuff on your captioning.
Um you know, one of the things I like to do

