00:38:04.670 --> 00:38:08.460
[Joe] How do you prioritize clients?

00:38:08.460 --> 00:38:16.329
[Mike] How, I'm trying to parse the question,
so I'm I'm I'm guessing, they're mean like,

00:38:16.329 --> 00:38:21.260
how do you work with clients to make sure
