00:38:21.260 --> 00:38:25.430
can do your job.
You know SEO, like that balance between what

00:38:25.430 --> 00:38:28.569
the client copy wants and then also what the
project requires.

00:38:28.569 --> 00:38:34.910
[Joe] Yeah yeah, so so that's a difficult
