at all um,
unless that hashtag was something that you

00:41:03.291 --> 00:41:10.730
think people are gonna search for on image
search uh, but I don't really see that. I

00:41:10.730 --> 00:41:18.960
mean, like like I said before, you really
have to understand your query um your query

00:41:18.960 --> 00:41:28.440
uh intention and you know you're you're, what
is the, you know motive behind searching uh

00:41:28.440 --> 00:41:34.780
query intent, you know. And if, if you think
that users are going to be searching on image

00:41:34.780 --> 00:41:41.700
search uh for a hashtag, then yeah you can
