00:42:03.260 --> 00:42:05.270
then absolutely do that, you know.

00:42:05.270 --> 00:42:10.960
[Mike] Sure, um we have a few more minutes
so I'm gonna ask a question that I have that

00:42:10.960 --> 00:42:17.829
I wondering your thoughts on. Do does, do
TLDs affect the SEO, because you got there's

