00:43:21.030 --> 00:43:28.619
that. It's like in commonplace, you know,
uh language now. So you know all these other

00:43:28.619 --> 00:43:36.869
TLDs uh it's hard to explain to people that
that might be linking to you, but oh no it's

00:43:36.869 --> 00:43:41.170
not .com,
it's .market or you know something that they

00:43:41.170 --> 00:43:47.800
maybe didn't even know existed, you know.
Um and so I would say that you know from a,

00:43:47.800 --> 00:43:54.770
from a, technical standpoint no you know,
TLD doesn't really matter too much um. It

00:43:54.770 --> 00:43:58.720
does matter though from a practical standpoint
